{"id":"kb-001","title":"油皮和痘肌更适合清爽型防晒","category":"sunscreen","tags":["防晒","油皮","痘肌","清爽"],"product_ids":["sun-001"],"concerns":["uv_protection","anti_acne"],"skin_types":["oily","combination","acne_prone"],"ingredients":["zinc oxide","niacinamide","centella"],"scenarios":["daily","summer"],"finish_preferences":["light"],"evidence_type":"general","content":"油皮、混油皮和痘肌在选择防晒时，通常更适合轻薄、成膜快、不厚重的产品。带有控油、低刺激和不易闷痘特征的防晒，更容易兼顾通勤舒适度和长期使用体验。"}
{"id":"kb-002","title":"干敏肌更看重屏障支持和保湿型防晒","category":"sunscreen","tags":["防晒","干皮","敏感肌","保湿"],"product_ids":["sun-002"],"concerns":["uv_protection","hydrating","barrier_support"],"skin_types":["dry","sensitive"],"ingredients":["ceramide","panthenol","squalane"],"scenarios":["daily","sensitive_period","winter"],"finish_preferences":["glowy"],"evidence_type":"general","content":"干皮和敏感肌在防晒选择上，往往更关注保湿、舒缓和屏障支持。含有神经酰胺、泛醇、角鲨烷等成分的防晒，更适合在屏障脆弱或换季时期使用。"}
{"id":"kb-003","title":"烟酰胺适合控油提亮与痘肌维稳","category":"serum","tags":["精华","烟酰胺","控油","提亮"],"product_ids":["ser-001","base-001"],"concerns":["oil_control","brightening","anti_acne","barrier_support"],"skin_types":["oily","combination","acne_prone"],"ingredients":["niacinamide","zinc pca"],"scenarios":["daily"],"finish_preferences":["light","matte"],"evidence_type":"general","content":"烟酰胺常见于控油、提亮和维稳类产品，对混油皮、油皮和痘肌更友好。搭配温和保湿体系时，既能减少油光感，也能兼顾肤感和耐受性。"}
{"id":"kb-004","title":"神经酰胺和泛醇适合修护型精华与面霜","category":"repair","tags":["修护","神经酰胺","泛醇","屏障"],"product_ids":["ser-002","mois-002","sun-002"],"concerns":["barrier_support","hydrating","soothing"],"skin_types":["dry","sensitive"],"ingredients":["ceramide","panthenol","cholesterol"],"scenarios":["sensitive_period","winter"],"finish_preferences":["glowy"],"evidence_type":"repair","content":"神经酰胺、胆固醇和泛醇常见于修护型护肤品，适合干燥、敏感、泛红或屏障不稳定的人群。它们更偏向稳定肤况，而不是追求高刺激的速效功效。"}
{"id":"kb-005","title":"混油皮通勤底妆更适合轻薄雾面路线","category":"foundation","tags":["底妆","混油皮","雾面","通勤"],"product_ids":["base-001"],"concerns":["long_wear","oil_control","light_coverage"],"skin_types":["oily","combination"],"ingredients":["silica","niacinamide"],"scenarios":["daily","summer"],"finish_preferences":["light","matte"],"evidence_type":"general","content":"如果是混油皮或油皮，且使用场景偏通勤，轻薄雾面、控油和持妆通常比高光泽奶油肌更稳妥。尤其在长时间带妆场景下，雾面路线通常更容易保持整洁妆面。"}
{"id":"kb-006","title":"干皮底妆通常更适合偏润泽的底妆产品","category":"foundation","tags":["底妆","干皮","光泽","滋润"],"product_ids":["base-002"],"concerns":["hydrating"],"skin_types":["dry","normal","sensitive"],"ingredients":["hyaluronic acid","panthenol"],"scenarios":["daily","dating","winter"],"finish_preferences":["glowy"],"evidence_type":"general","content":"干皮、中性皮和部分敏感肌在底妆选择上，常常更偏向带有保湿感和光泽感的产品。此类产品在贴肤度和舒适度上通常更有优势，但对油皮和痘肌未必友好。"}
{"id":"kb-007","title":"敏感肌选品时可优先考虑无香精低刺激路线","category":"safety","tags":["敏感肌","香精","低刺激"],"product_ids":["sun-001","ser-001","ser-002","mois-001","base-001"],"concerns":["soothing","barrier_support"],"skin_types":["sensitive"],"ingredients":["fragrance"],"scenarios":["daily","sensitive_period"],"finish_preferences":[],"evidence_type":"safety","content":"对于敏感肌，优先考虑无香精、低刺激和配方简洁的产品通常更稳妥。即便产品定位温和，也建议先做局部试用，再观察肤感与耐受。"}
{"id":"kb-008","title":"痘肌更适合循序渐进地搭建清爽护肤方案","category":"safety","tags":["痘肌","清爽","维稳"],"product_ids":["sun-001","ser-001","mois-001"],"concerns":["anti_acne","barrier_support"],"skin_types":["acne_prone","oily","combination"],"ingredients":["niacinamide","centella","ectoin"],"scenarios":["daily","summer"],"finish_preferences":["light"],"evidence_type":"safety","content":"痘肌更适合从清爽、低刺激、维稳导向的护肤组合开始，避免一次叠加太多高活性产品。先建立稳定的清洁、保湿和防晒基础，再逐步增加功能型产品，通常更不容易翻车。"}
